data.description: Idyllic setting for this Charming Farmette . Original  1909  Snow Hill Manor House.  Beautifully renovated farmhouse with large wraparound porch. Gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances. Beautiful wood burning fireplace. Coffered ceilings. Hardwood floors throughout. Large sunlit bonus room on third level with vaulted ceilings. Hot Tub.  One year old whole house generator w/ 10 year warranty. Underground electric dog fence. Pastures with Black board fencing, barn and two run ins. (2) Automatic waterers in pastures. Water and electric to barn. New Gunite Pool. Charming  one bedroom apartment above the detached garage is currently rented. Adjoining 2 acre lot available for purchase mls#VAFQ2010320
